{"tid":1002555,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"‎‎PS4機主討論區(24) 好多Game仲未玩","createTime":"2019-01-31T04:40:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-31T05:47:23.000Z","uid":4502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"22801564d19178c477d0134db76f6b67f18453ea","tid":1002555,"uid":4502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T04:40:59.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">LIHKG-PS4機主討論區</span></strong></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/06/012523_3f43176ba19566ee7d979dfc1a578557.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F06%2F012523_3f43176ba19566ee7d979dfc1a578557.jpg&h=5a1f7134&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Welcome to PlayStation 4 Group.<br />\n歡迎加入PlayStation 4 大家庭。</span></strong><br />\n建議新加入的玩家首先細閱下文，如再有任何除購買主機以外的問題，歡迎提出。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">想查詢購買PS4主機問題，請到友Post查詢及討論。</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/-Q1efj34UB7k/Vz8WgIVLRcI/AAAAAAAAAVM/mb31eJHzvZczjlbjNgJUhIyFPb5QVcIogCLcB/s0/ps4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flh3.googleusercontent.com%2F-Q1efj34UB7k%2FVz8WgIVLRcI%2FAAAAAAAAAVM%2Fmb31eJHzvZczjlbjNgJUhIyFPb5QVcIogCLcB%2Fs0%2Fps4.gif&h=72218ae4&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">常見PlayStation Q &amp; A</span></strong></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">新機主必睇區：</span></div><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Q1.</span> PSN 同PS Plus有咩關係？<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">A1.</span> PSN即係PlayStation&trade;Network，其實係由Sony PlayStation&trade;提供的個人帳戶，呢個帳戶在PS4上只用作分辨使用者從而使用其儲檔及設定。而一般玩家所以及的PlayStation&reg;Plus(部份人搞錯為PSN Plus，實為PS Plus)，是由Sony PlayStation&trade;提供的個人帳戶升級服務，當中包括多人線上遊玩，每月免費遊戲，優先預享特權以及自動下載更新及在線資料備份等等。<br />\n詳細有關PS Plus的介紹請往下面連結：<br />\n<a href=\"https://asia.playstation.com/cht-hk/psn/#overiew\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fasia.playstation.com%2Fcht-hk%2Fpsn%2F%23overiew&d=h41GIreLF%2BIJLuW8J2uc6j%2BzTm40CM4Hl%2BPVqeZuRg0%3D&h=7d6a3db5\" target=\"_blank\">https://asia.playstation.com/cht-hk/psn/#overiew</a><br />\n每月PS Plus所提供的免費遊戲及其他優惠可前往下面網頁下載：<br />\n<a href=\"https://asia.playstation.com/cht-hk/latest-news/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fasia.playstation.com%2Fcht-hk%2Flatest-news%2F&d=h41GIreLF%2BIJLuW8J2uc6j%2BzTm40CM4Hl%2BPVqeZuRg0%3D&h=761fdb0d\" target=\"_blank\">https://asia.playstation.com/cht-hk/latest-news/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://asia.playstation.com/cht-hk/psn/playstation-plus/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fasia.playstation.com%2Fcht-hk%2Fpsn%2Fplaystation-plus%2F&d=h41GIreLF%2BIJLuW8J2uc6j%2BzTm40CM4Hl%2BPVqeZuRg0%3D&h=477e7fa8\" target=\"_blank\">https://asia.playstation.com/cht-hk/psn/playstation-plus/</a><br />\n**(就算未有PS3，PSVita，PS4，只可一日擁有PS Plus，你都可以用上面網頁預先下載)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Q2.</span> PS Plus會藉可否累積上去？<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">A2.</span> 可以，例子：你會藉到下一年一月完，你在本年五月購買多次12個月會藉，會藉完結日期會由下一年一月增加12個月到後一年一月。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">**(用信用卡續會請緊記要<strong>自行取消自動續約</strong>，並且建議所有玩家使用雙重認證。)</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Q3.</span> 啱啱成為機主，點登記保養？<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">A3.</span> 請按下方連結前往登記頁面<br />\n<a href=\"https://asia.playstation.com/cht-hk/support/warranty-services/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fasia.playstation.com%2Fcht-hk%2Fsupport%2Fwarranty-services%2F&d=h41GIreLF%2BIJLuW8J2uc6j%2BzTm40CM4Hl%2BPVqeZuRg0%3D&h=9e6c368b\" target=\"_blank\">https://asia.playstation.com/cht-hk/support/warranty-services/</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Q4.</span> PS4保養有無得加長？<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">A4.</span> 可以用官方價$298於藍店或Sony Shop購買加長保養卡，但保養加強服務只限PS4主機，不包括手制及其他配件如Camera及VR。<br />\n網上登記保養另外送90日保養服務，所以最長保養期為2年連90日。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Q5.</span> PS4用wifi定用LAN線直插線上網？<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">A5.</span> 首選LAN線，穩定好多<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Q6.</span> 咩係藍店 <br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">A6.</span> 即係PlayStation Platinum Shop，<br />\n另有Sony Store和特許經銷商出售PS4及其遊戲<br />\n可以去下面網頁查詢各店舖位置<br />\n<a href=\"https://asia.playstation.com/cht-hk/support/retail-store/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fasia.playstation.com%2Fcht-hk%2Fsupport%2Fretail-store%2F&d=h41GIreLF%2BIJLuW8J2uc6j%2BzTm40CM4Hl%2BPVqeZuRg0%3D&h=250ca81e\" target=\"_blank\">https://asia.playstation.com/cht-hk/support/retail-store/</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Q7.</span> 數位版遊戲係唔係load得快過實體碟遊戲？<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">A7.</span> 其實兩者讀取時間一樣，分別只在於遊戲認證時會連接PSN網絡作認證還是以實體碟光碟作認證。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Q8.</span> 咁我應該買數位版定實體碟？<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">A8.</span> 好視乎個人習慣而定。<br />\n數位版好處係當需要換遊戲時唔使更換光碟就可以直接啟動另一款遊戲，以及沒有運作光碟相應較安靜，但無法隨意出售所擁有的數位版遊戲；<br />\n而實體碟則可以在無需要PSN網絡之下進行單機認證及進行單人遊戲，以及可以輕鬆出售所擁有的遊戲實體碟，但需要空間儲存遊戲光碟和更換遊戲時需連同光碟更換。<br />\n<br />\n個人建議喺兩種情況下會選擇數位版：<br />\n當該款遊戲只提供線上遊戲而完全沒有任何單機/單人模式。<br />\n當該款遊戲會不時存取來進行遊玩，如經常會被邀請遊玩的遊戲，或知道定期會出DLC的遊戲。"},{"pid":"4d33187908dd181ee0d16d31e7111c5f37de21a5","tid":1002555,"uid":87546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T04:41:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>除左PS4我仲係XB1手足.....<br />\n原本諗住做埋SWITCH手足<br />\n不過諗諗下都係不了</blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"